{"tid":1113877,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"每一個人都有等待被說出的故事","createTime":"2019-04-18T07:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T20:19:51.000Z","uid":47727,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da32371b43f65023e5ff4ea814c30d6fb4be899b","tid":1113877,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:28:12.000Z","msg":"是咁的，先介紹一下我自己，我是一名紋身師，同時亦是一個以畫面記錄故事的人。<br />\n<br />\n一直都認為每一個人都是如此不同，心裏面都有一些等待被說出的故事。很多時都想着要被記錄，或是紀念，時刻提醒着自己。以文字敘述的故事或是一句句子，甚至乎是一個有象徵的畫面。<br />\n<br />\n係感情台睇得耐有感而發，想聽下大家講下自己一個一直想講嘅故事，我會嘗試畫出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n但係我只會選擇地去畫，千祈唔好催。"},{"pid":"771f235b4f7e38a2626a39fc9cdf804502576f3b","tid":1113877,"uid":187295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"想紋字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b281ebcb8544d598664b4eedd8fbbfa3411e613c","tid":1113877,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"771f235b4f7e38a2626a39fc9cdf804502576f3b","tid":1113877,"uid":187295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"想紋字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:35:54.000Z","msg":"可以啊，分享下你嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739935d323c4586ad9f1145ba1e45c42ca77a951","tid":1113877,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"開呢一個主題嘅時候其實係覺得好多人紋身都只不過係想紋一啲覺得靚嘅圖案，但係卻沒有太故事在內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然好睇嘅圖案，好多時都包含一些自己嘅感覺，但其實我想傾聽更加多，可以讓圖案更加豐富有故事。"},{"pid":"7a0e5820e091dde3f63388b851e76b46fc70322c","tid":1113877,"uid":47727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T08:02:00.000Z","msg":"以畫面記錄故事，冇人有興趣咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.g